::Squizzy::

She finished her tests and started to clean the lab up where she had been 
working.  She went to the corner  to put some stuff away, when she found an 
old, dusty DNA replicator regenerator.  She wiped the dust off and read the 
name from the small digital read out panel.  Her eyes grew wide a she saw 
the name.  "It can't be so. I thought they would have gotten rid of her by 
now. But here she is."  She pressed a few buttons and started up the 
machine.  The statis on the bot inside as complete and the bot was 
functional.  She smiled and ran a check on it's programs. They were just as 
they had been.  She opened her link to the commander. "UH, excuse me Sir. 
But I have something that might be of interest to you. Uh, when you have a 
moment commander, I'd like to speak to you."
